="/wiki/Code-switching_(disambiguation)" class="mw-disambig" title="Code-switching (disambiguation)">Code-switching (disambiguation)</a>.</div>\n<table class="vertical-navbox nowraplinks plainlist" style="float:right;clear:right;width:22.0em;margin:0 0 1.0em 1.0em;background:#f9f9f9;border:1px solid #aaa;padding:0.2em;border-spacing:0.4em 0;text-align:center;line-height:1.4em;font-size:88%;width:18.0em;">\n<tr>\n<th style="background:#66ccff;;padding:0.2em 0.4em 0.2em;font-size:145%;line-height:1.2em;border-bottom:5px solid whitesmoke;"><a href="/wiki/Sociolinguistics" title="Sociolinguistics">Sociolinguistics</a></th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th style="padding:0.1em;background:#66ccff;">Key concepts</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="padding:0 0.1em 0.4em;padding:0.25em 0 0.5em;font-size:105%;">\n<ul>\n<li><a class="mw-selflink selflink">Code-switching</a></li>\n<li><a href="/wiki/Diglossia" title="Diglossia">Diglossia</a></li>\n<li><a href="/wiki/Language_change" title="Language change">Language change</a></li>\n<li><a href="/wiki/Language_ideology" title="Language ideology">Language ideology</a></li>\n<li><a href="/wiki/Language_planning" title="Language planning">Language planning</a></li>\n<li><a href="/wiki/Multilingualism" title="Multilingualism">Multilingualism</a></li>\n<li><a href="/wiki/Prestige_(sociolinguistics)" title="Prestige (sociolinguistics)">Prestige</a></li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th style="padding:0.1em;background:#66ccff;">Areas of study</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="padding:0 0.1em 0.4em;padding:0.25em 0 0.5em;font-size:105%;">\n<ul>\n<li><a href="/wiki/Accent_(sociolinguistics)" title="Accent (sociolinguistics)">Accent</a></li>\n<li><a href="/wiki/Dialect" title="Dialect">Dialect</a></li>\n<li><a href="/wiki/Register_(sociolinguistics)" title="Register (sociolinguistics)">Register</a></li>\n<li><a href="/wiki/Discourse_analysis" title="Discourse analysis">Discourse analysis</a></li>\n<li><a href="/wiki/Variety_(linguistics)" title="Variety (linguisti